DESCRIPTION: 

  After forgot password flow user can login with old and new password
  
PRECONDITIONS: 

  User is logged in with the password sent by email after completing forgot password flow
  
STEPS TO REPRODUCE:

1.  Logout from user profile
2.  Open login form
3.  Enter valid email 
4.  Enter old password 
5.  Click on "PRIJAVA" button

EXPECTED RESULT:

  Error message is displayed 
  
ACTUAL RESULT: 
  User is logged in with old password
  
NOTE: 

  User can login with old and new password multiple times
